DEATHTROID
============

What?
----------
Deathmatch multiplayer Metroid.

Deps
----------
- pyglets  http://pyopengl.sourceforge.net/
- pyopengl http://pyopengl.sourceforge.net/

Installing Deps
----------
easy_install pyglet
easy_install pyopengl

And how do I run it?
----------
With menu:

- `python main.py`

From commandline:

- `python main.py [username] both` # to start server and join it
- `python main.py [username] client [host]` # to connect to a game

